text:
Base ImmutableTableLocationKey implementation for table locations that may be enclosed by partitions and
 described by a File.
 Sub-classes should override compareTo(TableLocationKey) and equals(Object) only if they need to
 prevent equality with other FileTableLocationKey implementations.
